Default plot types for the verification metrics in the EVS.

          Description

Interface Summary
EVSPlot An interface for EVS plots.
EVSThresholdPlot Identifies a plot that shows data for a series of threshold values.
RealValuedPlot Interface that identifies a plot that contains real units on one or more axes and a method for setting those units.
ScoreDecompositionPlot Identifies a plot that comprises a score decomposition.
